with brain tumors with very favorable results.
CONCLUSION: Improving delivery of agents to the brain will play a major role in 
the therapeutic outcome of brain neoplasms. As techniques for gene therapy are 
advanced, manipulation of the BBB also may be important in the treatment of 
central nervous system genetic disorders.

